data.description: ***Seller is offering 2/1 rate buy-down! *** Welcome to the epitome of elegance and comfort in the prestigious Wyboo Plantation. This stunning home offers the perfect blend of modern amenities and serene natural beauty, golf course vistas and the added convenience of a private boat slip. With a recent kitchen renovation, this property is a dream come true for those who appreciate the finer things in life. This spacious floor plan seamlessly blends the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen is the heart of the home and has been thoughtfully updated with gleaming quartz, providing ample space for meal preparation and entertaining.
